::Hevn::
       "What the blazes...?"  He shakes his head again.  "I missed on 
purpose, and what does she do, fly into the shots.  By the pit she is an odd one, oh 
well.  So it goes."  He looks around and realizes he's lost track of 
Blackstorm in the commotion.  He sends a brief message to her.  "Hello Blackstorm, 
could you do me a favor and send me your coordinates, I have a brief message to 
relay to you that is best delivered in person."
